            "title": "即月期指開報23570點 低水71點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報23570點，升53點，較上日現貨收市價23640點低水71點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5381點，跌不足1點，低水不足1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報8583點，升16點，低水10點。</p>\n</div>",
